Lawrence A. Bowes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lawrence_A._Bowes 0 Lawrence A. Bowes (1 January 1885 – 5 June 1955) was an American actor. He appeared in 22 films between 1915 and 1921. He was born in Newark, California, United States and died in Glendale, California. Lawrence_A._Bowes ( 1_January_1885 – 5_June_1955 ) was an_American_actor .
